            <title>[AMQ-1613] Inactivity monitor blocks trying to close out a Failover transport that is in the middle of send.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-1613</link>
                <project id="12311210" key="AMQ">ActiveMQ Classic</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The net affect of this is that clients don&apos;t get reconnected within the inactivity monitor configured time.  They have to wait for the OS socket to notice the connection failure to reconnect.  This in effect is making the inactivity monitor in-effective for heavily used connections.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
